City travel = VIP click (no accidental teleports); Studio VIP; debug readout

- The "Go to City" pad teleported on TOUCH, so walking near the plot entrance
  yanked you to the city repeatedly — making the plot feel unusable (likely behind
  the "upgrade/purchase stopped working" report). It's now a CLICK, and the instant
  teleport is VIP-gated (non-VIP told to walk/drive). "Back to Stadium" pads are
  clicks too. No more accidental teleports.
- Studio now grants VIP (alongside test coins) so VIP-gated features are testable.
- Re-added a small top-right debug readout (coins/gems/stands + last server msg) to
  pin down the purchase/upgrade report on the plot. Will remove once confirmed.

